snippet.description:

Watch reveal trailer of Density Limit, a NightCat Studios game

#DensityLimit #​MidnightShow2022 #NightCatStudios​
Follow us:
Website: https://nightcatstudios.com​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/nightcatstudios​
Discord: https://go.nightcatstudios.com/discord

About Density Limit:
Welcome to the whole new world! It has a lot of names but we call it the Unspace. We're not gonna lie, it’s a little scary there, but it’s very attractive for scientists and kind of mysterious as well. But what is the limit of this space? What happened here and why does it even exist? And what’s more exciting is why it’s so messed up? Your mission will be to solve this case.

About NightCat Studios:
We are a multidirectional creative studio founded in Ukraine in 2017. We do everything we'd like to create: author original games, movies, music and in future there will be more.
